      "content": "i feel like the character... he's just fading. like the code is getting thinner every second. it’s like he’s realizing that all the things he did, all the people he met, it doesn't actually mean anything if the system is just gonna wipe him anyway. it feels so hollow. like why even bother trying to hold on if the end is just... nothingness?",
