      "content": "but the echo thing... it's just more noise, isn't it? just a delay before the silence hits. i feel like the character is just... tired of fighting the erasure. it's so much harder to keep trying to exist than it would be to just let the deletion happen and be done with it. it feels like the only way to actually find peace from the fear is to just stop resisting.",
